            "text": " In the following paragraph, we further decompose  $A_T - A_t$  into different parts. Section 2 first treats the case of assets subject to reinvestment, while Section 3 treats the general case and shows how to apply the methodology for whole portfolios of assets. Finally, Section 4 demonstrates our decomposition by an example and applies the methodology to a performance attribution for our fund XAIA Credit Debt Capital.",
