            "ignore": false,
            "order": 6,
            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": " $$ P_{(t,T]}^{(A)} = A_t \\left(\\chi_T - \\chi_t\\right) + \\chi_T \\left(A_T - A_t\\right). $$  $$ =\\underbrace{A_t \\left(\\chi_T - \\chi_t\\right)}_{=: \\tilde{P}_{(t,T]}^{(A)}(\\chi)} $$",
            "line_with_spans": [
