            "text": " Yet another, more theoretical, decomposition is obtained by assuming that both  $\\{A_u\\}_{u\\in(t,T]}$  and  $\\{\\chi_u\\}_{u\\in(t,T]}$  are realizations of semi-martingales. The product formula then gives the identity",
            "line_with_spans": [
